xxl.core.comparators
Class EmbeddingComparator<T>

java.lang.Object
  xxl.core.comparators.EmbeddingComparator<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of the objects to be compared with this comparator.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparator<T>
public class EmbeddingComparator<T>
extends Object
implements Comparator<T>, Serializable

The EmbeddingComparator adds a bound to a given comparator.

See Also:
Comparator, Serialized Form
